ctpp2 (2.8.3-4) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  [ Vasudev Kamath ]
  * Fix libctpp2-2.symbols file by replacing architecture dependent
    symbols with demangled symbols tagged as (c++).
    Closes: bug#705135.
  * Pass -v$(DEB_UPSTREAM_VERSION) to dpkg-gensymbols to avoid it
    including Debian versions in symbols file.
  * Add patch 1004 to skip iconv on kFreeBSD and the Hurd: Fixes FTBFS.
    Closes: bug#705134
  * Use canonical anonscm.d.o field for Vcs-Git field.

  [ Jonas Smedegaard ]
  * Add README.source emphasizing control.in file as *not* a
    show-stopper for contributions, referring to wiki page for details.

